"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/801136","Ministry of Defence","false","2017-12-13","<p>Following the publication of the Government's Civil Service Diversity and Inclusion Strategy in October 2017 the Department's new strategic objectives are in the process of being finalised and will be published in due course.</p>","Bournemouth East","Mr Tobias Ellwood",,"2017-12-13T15:00:00.567Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/801136/answer","Biography information for Mr Tobias Ellwood","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/801136/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/801136/answer",,,,,"11","Defence","Defence","2017-12-05","Ministry of Defence: Equality","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Defence, pursuant to the Answer of 26 June 2017 to Question 438, when his Department plans to publish its new strategic equality objectives.","false","Biography information for Nia Griffith","Llanelli","Nia Griffith","117695"
