"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/800530","Ministry of Defence","false","2017-12-13","<p>In the past 12 months no VIP flights on VIP-configured RAF Voyager aircraft have been diverted from their intended destinations due to technical issues.</p>","West Worcestershire","Harriett Baldwin",,"2017-12-13T14:55:47.117Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/800530/answer","Biography information for Harriett Baldwin","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/800530/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/800530/answer",,,,,"11","Defence","Defence","2017-12-04","Future Strategic Tanker Aircraft","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Defence, on how many occasions in the past 12 months flights on VIP-configured RAF Voyager aircraft have been diverted from their intended destinations due to technical issues.","false","Biography information for Mr Kevan Jones","North Durham","Mr Kevan Jones","117151"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/800531","Ministry of Defence","false","2017-12-13","<p>Government Departments provide transparency releases on the gov.uk website concerning the costs and details of Ministerial transport on a regular basis.</p><p>In addition the Royal Household publish the costs and details of Royal Travel as an Annex to the Royal Household Annual Financial reports that are published on the royal.uk website.</p>","West Worcestershire","Harriett Baldwin",,"2017-12-13T14:52:40.087Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/800531/answer","Biography information for Harriett Baldwin","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/800531/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/800531/answer",,,,,"11","Defence","Defence","2017-12-04","Future Strategic Tanker Aircraft","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Defence, what the cost of operating VIP configured RAF Voyager aircraft was in the last 12 months.","false","Biography information for Mr Kevan Jones","North Durham","Mr Kevan Jones","117152"
